*        GENERAL DESCRIPTION
*        THE ZZLABL SUBROUTINE WILL GIVE THE LABEL NUMBER AND THE
*        VOLUME SERIAL OF A TAPE SPECIFIED FOR A GIVEN DDNAME.
*        CALLING PROCEDURE
*              CALL 'ZZLABL' USING WAAX-DDNAME WABB-LABEL.
*        05 WAAX-DDNAME  PICTURE X(8).
*        05 WABB-LABEL   PICTURE S9(9) COMP SYNC.
*        NOTES
*        THE DDNAME IS SUPPLIED BY THE CALLING PROGRAM. THE LABEL
*        NUMBER AND THE VOLUME SERIAL IS SUPPLIED BY THE SUBROUTINE.
*        THE VOLUME SERIAL IS PLACED IN THE DDNAME FIELD AND IS LEFT
*        ALIGNED.
ZZLABL   CSECT
         IN    12,PARM=YES
         REGEQ
         LM    R3,R4,0(R1)
         USING  IHADCB,R2
         LA    R2,IN
         MVC   DCBDDNAM,0(R3)
         RDJFCB IN
         LH    R6,JFCB+68
         ST    R6,0(R4)
         MVC   0(6,R3),JFCB+118
         MVC   6(2,R3),=C'  '
         OUT   0
IN       DCB   DSORG=PS,MACRF=GL,EXLST=X
         DS    0D
X        DC    X'87',AL3(JFCB)
JFCB     DS    CL176
         LTORG
         DCBD   DSORG=PS
         END
